CS SAMAS RPA Pilot
Elite Coalition pilot trained to operate the PA-06A SAMAS power armor. SAMAS
pilots combine aerial mobility with heavy firepower and are among the most
recognizable symbols of CS military dominance on Rifts Earth.

Starting skills: Pilot SAMAS power armor, weapon systems, W.P. energy rifle,
radio basic, military etiquette, detect ambush, plus elective picks from
Pilot, Pilot Related, Military, Technical, and W.P. categories.

Attribute requirements: IQ 10, PP 11.
Starting equipment: SAMAS power armor (CS military issue), C-20 laser pistol,
TX-5 particle beam rifle, radio headset, and CS support package.
Starting credits: 200 to 1200 credits (2d6 x 100).
PPE / ISP: No starting PPE or ISP.

